00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:47,560
 And what is this sound?

36
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:58,180
 I can't talk and only strange sounds are coming out.

37
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:19,700
 I can't remember anything.

38
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:24,900
 Who I am or why I am here.

39
00:07:25,690 --> 00:07:31,490
 And... where I need to go.

40
00:07:31,490 --> 00:07:36,190

41
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:47,500
Please stay still!  You keep shaking.

42
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:49,630
Aren't you done yet?

43
00:07:51,970 --> 00:07:53,370
Isn't it suspicious?

44
00:07:53,370 --> 00:07:57,150
Why does a man living alone have women's clothes?

45
